title: Wentz's debut & QB rankings
itunes:title: Wentz's debut & QB rankings
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Colleen Wolfe -- discuss the latest news including Tyrod Taylor's contract extension. The heroes then break down the first day of preseason games including Paxton Lynch's debut for Denver. They wrap the show by examining ESPN's recent quarterback rankings.
